Two Types of Storage
Object Storage
GET/PUT/DELETE
Used for storing images, datafiles, documents etc.
AWS S3, GS, Swift
______________________|
File/Block Storage
Creating filesystems in containers /etc/nginx
Examples: AWS EBS, NFS, Cinder, Gluster, iSCSI, SAN
______________________|
Native Cloud Architecture
Persistence must happen somewhere
Resiliency is usually baked into the application
12 Factor App
